{"tid":820202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港最高級別警告：巨災警報","createTime":"2018-09-15T09:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T14:15:26.000Z","uid":98826,"like":187,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"4615814d68716f5dcbb57eddb0008885eee334f8","tid":820202,"uid":98826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:34:35.000Z","msg":"巨災警報<br />\n<br />\n全香港之消防員輪替或候命出動。災情警報亦適用於非火警、範圍廣闊、或一連串同時發生之災害事件，如大型民航客機墜毀於民居、人煙稠密的地區、工商大廈或者危險性高的建築則會立即列為災難級火警。而這一系列事件有跡象需長時間以全部資源參與，甚至或需要軍隊或其他單位（如香港民眾安全服務隊）協助。<br />\n<br />\n此警報只可由消防處處長指示之下，或由官階在區長級或以上之官員親自向處長要求後方可發出。至今香港只發出三次災情警報，均發生於1972年：分別是1月9日海上學府火災、6月18日暴雨導致中午秀茂坪（現在翠屏邨位置）嚴重山泥傾瀉及晚上西半山（旭龢道旭龢大廈）樓宇連環倒塌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/172731_5ea7cbe3a4dc4a44849905e0da1e646e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F172731_5ea7cbe3a4dc4a44849905e0da1e646e.png&h=75478aa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/173336_854b9c6d7f0e197ee30af60219d740d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F173336_854b9c6d7f0e197ee30af60219d740d0.png&h=3e9e82d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/香港火警分級制度\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%81%AB%E8%AD%A6%E5%88%86%E7%B4%9A%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6&d=bWgaZwBvmeazD3cCoRUlqUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=b6d662f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/香港火警分級制度</a>"},{"pid":"bb43d38d0035caed1b81b63f796fdb2260bfe6e1","tid":820202,"uid":99700,"like":480,"dislike":16,"score":464,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:44:12.000Z","msg":"吹大左啦 聽朝訓醒咪又係乜事都冇"},{"pid":"c8fa35b8be54c44221909aee0a18a80587de08b1","tid":820202,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751782a5133d9a980813715ef4ffe1ccc4d8f507","tid":820202,"uid":127929,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:45:10.000Z","msg":"啲樓起係山隔離真係幾危險下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc09289b9109c461fe26d6be195fe9f399d1cffb","tid":820202,"uid":51701,"like":7,"dislike":32,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"主題引起不安"},{"pid":"d19e5dedea2343f23e3dba03dca16b9e55633804","tid":820202,"uid":209792,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"香港人早D訓 星期一仲要返工"},{"pid":"0aa7809f9d1665fbefac5968c6c6438838e72035","tid":820202,"uid":81256,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:49:05.000Z","msg":"做咩啫你"},{"pid":"f5de49143d05c74b96f68278f54352cc8dcb3c4c","tid":820202,"uid":13724,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bb43d38d0035caed1b81b63f796fdb2260bfe6e1","tid":820202,"uid":99700,"like":480,"dislike":16,"score":464,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:44:12.000Z","msg":"吹大左啦 聽朝訓醒咪又係乜事都冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:51:43.000Z","msg":"聽朝應該未有事，聽日先嚟料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9009163de9d80118d89bc1c59ee31c98acf139","tid":820202,"uid":66811,"like":509,"dislike":9,"score":500,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9HTfO1o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9HTfO1o.png&h=ddb81907&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4c30418985401fea89a50b1c0e0d6e07c551002","tid":820202,"uid":137604,"like":1,"di